Package: splp
Type: Package
Title: Smooth Local Projections for Panel Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jackson", "Mejia", email = "jpmejia@pmit.edu",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Jackson Mejia <jpmejia@mit.edu>
Description: Implements smooth local projections for panel data. It extends the Barnichon &
    Brownlees (2019) ridge regression estimator for time series data into panel data. The
    package is a wrapper for fixest and uses the same notation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    data.table,
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
    splines,
    Matrix,
    fixest,
    ggplot2
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
